snippet.title: Living Waters For The World Project   Lady Dee And Amber Kaye   Kentucky Vocal Union
snippet.description:
ITSMONTEZDOTCOM
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC4B0rMa68o1WiXP58ATi3xA

So in this film Lady Dee and Amber Kay Talk about Time and Money and which is a great factor in their life's. Using the time that one has effectively can be quite hard to do if one dose not know what they quite want in life as you will here in this film By Lady Dee and Amber Kaye In this film you will view the Living Waters Guatemala Project Event  During the film Taste of Guatemala You will find out What it is and why it has been founded and what it is that the foundation dose 

Support the Living Waters Guatemala Project- helping to provide clean sustainable water to communities in Guatemala who have no clean drinking water- by attending "A Taste of Guatemala

https://www.facebook.com/LivingWatersGuatemalaProject/?fref=ts
Click this link to like the facebook page and support the cause! 

Elizabethtown Rotary and  First Presbyterian Church providing clean water in Guatemala.
http://www.etownpres.org/living-waters.html

https://hardinlocal.com/a-taste-of-guatemala/
https://hardinchamber.com/living-waters-guatemala-project/

https://hardinchamber.com/benefit-auction-to-benefit-living-waters-guatemala-project/

http://historicstatetheater.org/Calendar.asp


Picture
The Living Waters Guatemala Team has recently visited some 17 new communities in the western highlands of Guatemala.  Many had heard about the water systems we were installing from others who were already enjoying clean water.  They heard about the difference that clean water was making in the health of families receiving it.  They heard that the water was affordable and even free if you couldn’t pay.

http://www.livingwatersfortheworld.org/

if you  would like to support this channel you may do so but subscribing to this channel !
